  standards_of_creation = 'FSIS grant of inspection or state equivalent for mobile unit; mobile unit design approval documentation meeting FSIS construction standards; HACCP plan specific to mobile operations (addressing variable site conditions); water supply documentation for each processing location; waste disposal plan with approved methods per location; route and schedule documentation filed with inspection authority; equipment sanitation verification between locations; vehicle registration and DOT inspection records',
